1
00:00:15,230 --> 00:00:16,231
I love you.

2
00:00:20,663 --> 00:00:23,480
- Ms. Shen?
- Someone is at the window, looking at us.

3
00:00:23,743 --> 00:00:25,040
Tone! Look!

4
00:00:26,457 --> 00:00:27,960
Where did the mud come from?

5
00:00:28,177 --> 00:00:29,397
I have no idea, ma'am.

6
00:00:29,483 --> 00:00:30,484
Is my husband home?

7
00:00:30,570 --> 00:00:32,560
He was here at the same time as Mr. Term.

8
00:00:32,690 --> 00:00:34,520
I'm here to warn you about Tone.

9
00:00:34,710 --> 00:00:36,400
I saw her leaving the house the him every day.

10
00:00:36,543 --> 00:00:38,720
They're both young and it could lead to scandal.

11
00:00:38,810 --> 00:00:39,711
Honey?

12
00:00:39,723 --> 00:00:40,880
It's you?

13
00:00:41,003 --> 00:00:42,760
- Yes, it's me.
- Shin!

14
00:00:42,943 --> 00:00:44,320
You can't tell anyone about it.

15
00:00:44,450 --> 00:00:46,040
I need something to keep my mouth shut.

16
00:00:46,090 --> 00:00:47,091
How much money do you want?

17
00:00:47,100 --> 00:00:48,120
I don't want any money.

18
00:00:48,317 --> 00:00:50,400
When I sneaked up on both of you,

19
00:00:50,503 --> 00:00:52,560
- I want the same feeling.
- Shin!

20
00:00:52,817 --> 00:00:54,600
Don't you dare think of Ms. Shen in a dirty way!

21
00:00:54,717 --> 00:00:55,920
It's not Ms. Shen that I am talking about.

22
00:00:56,043 --> 00:00:57,200
I was thinking of doing it with you.

23
00:00:57,250 --> 00:00:58,320
One time.

24
00:00:58,510 --> 00:00:59,960
you would like it.

25
00:01:00,183 --> 00:01:02,200
Tomorrow night, you will do it with me

26
00:01:02,357 --> 00:01:03,440
the same as you did it with Ms. Shen.

27
00:01:03,460 --> 00:01:05,120
Otherwise, I could slip

28
00:01:05,153 --> 00:01:07,680
and tell everyone in this house.

29
00:01:18,950 --> 00:01:19,951
Hey!

30
00:01:20,818 --> 00:01:23,712
Are Tone and Shin waking up late today?

31
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:27,450
Did they got drunk last night?

32
00:01:28,747 --> 00:01:30,720
I'm not sure about Shin and I don't think Tone had a drink.

33
00:01:33,374 --> 00:01:34,592
Hey, everyone

34
00:01:35,771 --> 00:01:36,920
where is Shin?

35
00:01:37,419 --> 00:01:39,082
He promised me that

36
00:01:39,165 --> 00:01:40,700
he would help me with food offering this morning.

37
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:42,131
But he didn't show up.

38
00:01:43,435 --> 00:01:45,880
We haven't seen him either, ma'am. I will get him for you.

39
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,521
Tone, there you are.

40
00:01:50,398 --> 00:01:51,399
Where is Shin?

41
00:01:52,123 --> 00:01:53,124
He is still asleep?

42
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,840
He is not here anymore.

43
00:01:56,312 --> 00:01:57,313
What?

44
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:59,161
Well..

45
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,400
In the middle of last night,

46
00:02:01,838 --> 00:02:03,680
he cried and got homesick.

47
00:02:04,131 --> 00:02:05,840
Then he packed up and left.

48
00:02:06,435 --> 00:02:07,436
He did?

49
00:02:09,536 --> 00:02:10,720
He stayed with us for so long.

50
00:02:10,918 --> 00:02:12,400
I've never thought that he would be like this.

51
00:02:12,987 --> 00:02:14,360
He didn't even say goodbye to me.

52
00:02:17,051 --> 00:02:18,760
Did he say when he will return?

53
00:02:19,297 --> 00:02:20,880
He…he didn't say anything.

54
00:02:21,228 --> 00:02:22,680
Why did he behave like this?

55
00:02:23,211 --> 00:02:24,480
This is not nice of him.

56
00:02:25,097 --> 00:02:26,720
Who will take care of me then?

57
00:02:33,574 --> 00:02:36,040
Tone, you don't want your breakfast?

58
00:02:36,951 --> 00:02:38,560
I'm not hungry.

59
00:02:45,503 --> 00:02:48,100
Auntie? I thought Shin didn't get along with his family.

60
00:02:48,397 --> 00:02:50,460
Why did he want to go home all of a sudden?

61
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:53,766
People can change their minds.

62
00:02:54,187 --> 00:02:55,800
I'm glad that he isn't around.

63
00:02:55,915 --> 00:02:57,360
- So annoying this guy.
- You're right.

64
00:03:45,457 --> 00:03:46,640
You're scared me.

65
00:03:47,338 --> 00:03:48,339
I'm sorry.

66
00:03:49,310 --> 00:03:50,520
Where are you going, Ms. Shen?

67
00:03:51,022 --> 00:03:53,720
I want to go to the market, can you drive me?

68
00:03:54,832 --> 00:03:56,240
There is a strange sound coming from the car.

69
00:03:56,811 --> 00:03:58,320
I'm worried that there is something wrong with it.

70
00:03:59,184 --> 00:04:00,720
I am about to have a mechanic to look at it.

71
00:04:02,491 --> 00:04:03,492
What?

72
00:04:07,182 --> 00:04:09,760
You told me that this car is new and it won't be broken.

73
00:04:11,624 --> 00:04:13,480
I think there is something wrong.

74
00:04:14,355 --> 00:04:15,558
It should be fine tomorrow.

75
00:04:16,824 --> 00:04:17,825
I'm sorry.

76
00:04:21,104 --> 00:04:22,360
You need to get it fixed then.

77
00:04:22,946 --> 00:04:23,947
Yes, ma'am.

78
00:04:26,787 --> 00:04:27,788
Tone,

79
00:04:29,825 --> 00:04:30,826
Is everything okay?

80
00:04:31,976 --> 00:04:33,200
Why are you acting weird?

81
00:04:34,734 --> 00:04:35,735
I'm fine.

82
00:04:59,224 --> 00:05:00,600
-Chan.
- Yes, ma'am.

83
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:03,080
Call a three-wheel cart for me, tell him that I'm going to the market.

84
00:05:03,950 --> 00:05:05,800
Why don't you call Tone to give you a ride?

85
00:05:06,274 --> 00:05:08,360
He said that the car was broken, he was about to get it fixed.

86
00:06:57,838 --> 00:07:00,120
Mister? Can you stop here?

87
00:07:02,637 --> 00:07:03,638
Just a moment.

88
00:07:15,238 --> 00:07:17,240
What do you say? Should we keep going?

89
00:07:19,131 --> 00:07:21,960
I think this is my stop, you can go.

90
00:10:06,616 --> 00:10:08,000
Ouch! Ouch!

91
00:10:09,592 --> 00:10:11,680
- Ms. Shen?
- Ow!

92
00:10:11,972 --> 00:10:14,056
Ms. Shen! Ms. Shen!

93
00:10:14,222 --> 00:10:15,813
Are you okay?

94
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,800
- Please listen to me.
- Let me go.

95
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:20,701
Ms. Shen, please listen to me.

96
00:10:23,897 --> 00:10:24,898
Ms. Shen!

97
00:10:27,331 --> 00:10:28,760
Please listen to me.

98
00:10:31,044 --> 00:10:33,045
Ms. Shen! Ms. Shen!

99
00:10:33,267 --> 00:10:35,480
Ms. Shen! Ms. Shen!

100
00:10:37,566 --> 00:10:39,840
- You murdered Shin!
- Ms. Shen!

101
00:10:40,056 --> 00:10:41,157
Let me explain.

102
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:43,840
Shin was the one sneaked up on us at the cottage.

103
00:10:44,814 --> 00:10:47,120
He said that he would tell everyone about us.

104
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,840
But you told me that there was a cazy person

105
00:10:50,915 --> 00:10:52,240
sneaked up on us?

106
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,511
I lied to you.

107
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:56,241
I didn't want you to be worried.

108
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,000
That's why I said it.

109
00:10:58,041 --> 00:10:59,100
Actually, it was Shin.

110
00:10:59,174 --> 00:11:01,280
Did you have to murder him like that?

111
00:11:01,366 --> 00:11:02,440
He threatened me.

112
00:11:03,216 --> 00:11:05,280
He threatened to expose us to others.

113
00:11:06,251 --> 00:11:07,880
I didn't want you to be in trouble.

114
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,560
I didn't mean to kill him.

115
00:11:11,216 --> 00:11:13,760
We were in a fight, he fell to the grown and hit his head.

116
00:11:14,390 --> 00:11:15,760
I didn't kill him.

117
00:11:16,230 --> 00:11:17,831
But we were the cause of his death.

118
00:11:17,905 --> 00:11:19,760
He died because of us.

119
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:20,801
Ms. Shen.

120
00:11:21,380 --> 00:11:22,720
Don't blame yourself like that.

121
00:11:24,179 --> 00:11:25,360
Shin did it himself.

122
00:11:28,057 --> 00:11:29,560
We should hide in the car.

123
00:11:41,523 --> 00:11:43,200
What should we do next?

124
00:11:44,724 --> 00:11:46,160
What are we going to do?

125
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:50,520
Nobody knows about it

126
00:11:51,697 --> 00:11:53,240
but me and you.

127
00:11:55,590 --> 00:11:57,120
His body was buried deep in the woods.

128
00:11:58,192 --> 00:11:59,960
Nobody will find him here.

129
00:12:06,168 --> 00:12:07,480
I'm scared.

130
00:12:07,657 --> 00:12:09,560
I'm really scared, Tone.

131
00:12:18,736 --> 00:12:19,979
Don't be.

132
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:22,681
Don't be scared.

133
00:12:25,408 --> 00:12:26,480
I am right here.

134
00:12:30,816 --> 00:12:32,600
I won't get you in troubles.

135
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:46,300
I want you to know that

136
00:12:49,257 --> 00:12:50,760
I can do anything for you

137
00:12:53,534 --> 00:12:54,761
because I love you, Ms. Shen.

138
00:13:01,662 --> 00:13:02,663
I love you.

139
00:13:05,731 --> 00:13:06,732
I love you.

140
00:14:49,142 --> 00:14:50,243
Where is my tea?

141
00:14:51,366 --> 00:14:52,760
You want some tea, ma'am?

142
00:14:53,888 --> 00:14:55,000
Didn't you know?

143
00:14:55,878 --> 00:14:57,200
I need to have my tea

144
00:14:57,275 --> 00:14:59,080
after I eat fried food so it won't be too greasy.

145
00:15:00,139 --> 00:15:02,680
I'm sorry, ma'am. I'll brew some tea for you.

146
00:15:02,937 --> 00:15:04,080
Don't make it too strong.

147
00:15:06,680 --> 00:15:07,881
Since Shin was gone,

148
00:15:08,014 --> 00:15:10,115
nobody has performed their tasks the way I prefer.

149
00:15:11,118 --> 00:15:12,720
When will Shin come back?

150
00:15:12,819 --> 00:15:14,120
Why are you still waiting for his return?

151
00:15:14,456 --> 00:15:15,960
He may not come back anymore.

152
00:15:21,274 --> 00:15:22,275
Shen?

153
00:15:23,099 --> 00:15:24,100
Are you okay?

154
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:27,961
Perm,

155
00:15:29,361 --> 00:15:31,840
how do you know that Shin won't be coming back?

156
00:15:32,297 --> 00:15:33,700
Well, he left without saying goodbye.

157
00:15:33,920 --> 00:15:35,360
He must have thought that he would be gone for good.

158
00:15:35,437 --> 00:15:36,600
And he wouldn't see our faces again.

159
00:15:38,703 --> 00:15:40,320
I think you should recruit a new help.

160
00:15:41,912 --> 00:15:42,913
Shen should do it.

161
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:46,161
You didn't let her go to the kitchen anymore.

162
00:15:46,773 --> 00:15:48,366
Shen should accompany Mom instead.

163
00:15:49,411 --> 00:15:51,440
She would have something to do instead of asking a driver

164
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:52,760
to drive her places every day.

165
00:15:55,963 --> 00:15:56,964
What do you think, Shen?

166
00:15:57,100 --> 00:15:59,376
Do you think that Mom would like Shen to be around?

167
00:15:59,718 --> 00:16:01,200
If it were Rayrai, then I would believe so.

168
00:16:02,619 --> 00:16:04,974
Stop arguing already.

169
00:16:05,907 --> 00:16:07,520
I don't want anybody.

170
00:16:09,297 --> 00:16:10,800
I know Shin well.

171
00:16:11,304 --> 00:16:13,440
He hasn't received his latest payment yet.

172
00:16:13,710 --> 00:16:14,880
He won't leave us for sure.

173
00:16:15,531 --> 00:16:16,560
He will be back soon.

174
00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:34,240
When it is war time,

175
00:16:34,603 --> 00:16:38,400
they prepared a big army,

176
00:16:39,104 --> 00:16:42,400
including swords, spears, and firearms.'

177
00:16:42,438 --> 00:16:44,800
- 'Marching…'
- Oh my! Stop it.

178
00:16:44,970 --> 00:16:47,200
Can you recite it properly? With better rhythm?

179
00:16:48,499 --> 00:16:49,500
This is so annoying.

180
00:16:51,011 --> 00:16:52,012
Khunying?

181
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:56,500
This is a letter from Shin's family to him.

182
00:16:58,827 --> 00:16:59,828
What?

183
00:17:00,278 --> 00:17:01,960
Shin wasn't home?

184
00:17:02,662 --> 00:17:03,663
Let me see.

185
00:17:06,678 --> 00:17:08,180
I need to read his letter.

186
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:17,881
What is this?

187
00:17:19,896 --> 00:17:22,280
- I'm so confused.
- What is going on?

188
00:17:23,288 --> 00:17:25,347
Shin's mom sent him a letter.

189
00:17:25,657 --> 00:17:26,880
She told Shin

190
00:17:27,038 --> 00:17:29,800
to visit the family because he hasn't been home for months.

191
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:34,040
Shin was gone but he wasn't home either?

192
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:36,520
He could secretly date someone

193
00:17:36,601 --> 00:17:37,720
and they could elope together.

194
00:17:39,038 --> 00:17:41,160
I think we better write them a letter back,

195
00:17:41,299 --> 00:17:42,400
saying that he hasn't been with us anymore.

196
00:17:43,571 --> 00:17:44,840
So they won't waste their time searching for him.

197
00:17:52,997 --> 00:17:55,800
I have no idea that he could be this irresponsible.

198
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:01,240
- 'Soldiers are yelling…'
- Come on!

199
00:18:01,347 --> 00:18:03,700
Stop reciting already! I'm done listening to you.

200
00:19:07,272 --> 00:19:08,600
Who are you talking to?

201
00:19:13,320 --> 00:19:15,040
Shin told me that you had an affair with Tone.

202
00:19:15,907 --> 00:19:16,908
Is it true?

203
00:19:19,097 --> 00:19:20,520
Tell him, ma'am.

204
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:27,801
Please tell him.

205
00:19:29,801 --> 00:19:32,400
Tell him the truth.

206
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,880
Tell him that you had an affair with Tone.

207
00:19:37,814 --> 00:19:39,640
Tell him! Come on!

208
00:19:45,523 --> 00:19:46,524
What is going on?

209
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:50,601
I had a nightmare.

210
00:19:51,923 --> 00:19:52,924
About what?

211
00:19:53,811 --> 00:19:56,400
Nothing in particular.

212
00:19:58,840 --> 00:19:59,841
Go back to bed.

213
00:20:21,040 --> 00:20:22,160
It was just a nightmare.

214
00:20:23,700 --> 00:20:25,080
Don't dwell on it.

215
00:20:27,263 --> 00:20:29,700
I'm worried that people will find out about us.

216
00:20:31,779 --> 00:20:33,140
About what we do.

217
00:20:34,515 --> 00:20:35,720
And abuot Shin.

218
00:20:53,107 --> 00:20:54,720
I've been thinking about it for days.

219
00:20:59,027 --> 00:21:00,790
I don't think we should come here anymore.

220
00:21:05,358 --> 00:21:06,960
We should end it now.

221
00:21:07,857 --> 00:21:08,858
Why did you say that?

222
00:21:09,814 --> 00:21:11,080
There is nothing going on right now.

223
00:21:11,264 --> 00:21:13,320
But someone died because of us, Tone!

224
00:21:14,694 --> 00:21:16,240
Shin died because of us.

225
00:21:16,886 --> 00:21:19,200
- Don't you feel anything?
- Of course, I do.

226
00:21:21,624 --> 00:21:23,680
What if someone saw us someday?

227
00:21:23,912 --> 00:21:25,400
It will be another trouble to handle.

228
00:21:27,694 --> 00:21:29,187
Let it end this way.

229
00:21:29,476 --> 00:21:31,440
Don't cause any troubles.

230
00:21:35,736 --> 00:21:36,960
I love you.

231
00:21:48,454 --> 00:21:49,640
I love you, too.

232
00:21:54,939 --> 00:21:57,520
But our love is so wrong.

233
00:22:00,854 --> 00:22:02,760
Let it be just good memory

234
00:22:04,624 --> 00:22:06,720
that only us know about it.

235
00:22:09,035 --> 00:22:10,920
Do you want me to leave you just like that?

236
00:22:11,886 --> 00:22:14,600
- I can't do it.
- You never leave me.

237
00:22:18,808 --> 00:22:21,240
In fact, we have never belonged to each other from the start.

238
00:22:35,707 --> 00:22:36,880
Let's just call it off.

239
00:22:38,416 --> 00:22:39,520
From now on,

240
00:22:42,280 --> 00:22:44,360
we both will be just a master

241
00:22:45,646 --> 00:22:47,880
and a driver like it should have been,

242
00:22:50,462 --> 00:22:51,960
nothing more than that.

243
00:23:01,742 --> 00:23:03,280
♪ There is real love ♪

244
00:23:04,600 --> 00:23:05,691
♪ existed ♪

245
00:23:06,627 --> 00:23:07,628
♪ in this world. ♪

246
00:23:09,912 --> 00:23:11,613
♪ I will hug you ♪

247
00:23:12,286 --> 00:23:15,640
♪ and I won't let you lose your faith. ♪

248
00:23:17,806 --> 00:23:19,120
♪ I promise that ♪

249
00:23:19,886 --> 00:23:20,920
♪ I will protect you ♪

250
00:23:22,016 --> 00:23:23,720
♪ forever. ♪

251
00:23:25,536 --> 00:23:27,240
♪ Because I was born ♪

252
00:23:28,350 --> 00:23:29,351
♪ to love you ... ♪

253
00:23:29,355 --> 00:23:31,100
Stop doing this.

254
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:35,961
Let's go home.

255
00:23:39,504 --> 00:23:40,505
But I love you.

256
00:23:50,650 --> 00:23:51,718
I want to go home.

257
00:25:42,320 --> 00:25:44,320
You ate a lot today.

258
00:25:45,598 --> 00:25:46,640
It is good, isn't it?

259
00:26:08,888 --> 00:26:09,889
Ms. Shen?

260
00:26:11,059 --> 00:26:13,160
Ms. Shen, are you okay?

261
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:14,841
Ms. Shen!

262
00:26:15,800 --> 00:26:16,920
Are you okay?

263
00:26:22,163 --> 00:26:23,164
May I?

264
00:26:33,811 --> 00:26:34,812
All done.

265
00:26:34,814 --> 00:26:35,815
Thank you.

266
00:26:37,080 --> 00:26:38,400
Congratulations, Mr. Perm.

267
00:26:39,027 --> 00:26:40,028
Shen is pregnant.

268
00:26:41,774 --> 00:26:43,120
She is 2 months pregnant.

269
00:26:45,918 --> 00:26:47,779
I will prescribe her prenatal supplements

270
00:26:47,902 --> 00:26:49,720
and arrange appointments to check on her regularly.

271
00:26:52,817 --> 00:26:53,818
Thank you so much.

272
00:26:55,915 --> 00:26:56,916
Congratulations again.

273
00:26:58,454 --> 00:26:59,455
Chan,

274
00:26:59,632 --> 00:27:01,080
can you escort him out?

275
00:27:01,640 --> 00:27:02,641
Yes, sir.

276
00:28:03,990 --> 00:28:05,120
I really want to her

277
00:28:08,484 --> 00:28:09,640
if it's a girl

278
00:28:10,851 --> 00:28:12,080
or a boy.

279
00:28:16,800 --> 00:28:17,801
Perm.

280
00:28:19,428 --> 00:28:21,200
Doctor said that Shen is pregnant?

281
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:22,401
That's right.

282
00:28:22,700 --> 00:28:24,562
I'm so thrilled that I'm speechless.

283
00:28:27,211 --> 00:28:28,960
Oh my! My sweet angel.

284
00:28:29,480 --> 00:28:31,280
You're finally here.

285
00:28:33,003 --> 00:28:36,182
Shen, you need to take a good care of yourself.

286
00:28:36,464 --> 00:28:37,840
You are carrying my grandchild.

287
00:28:38,331 --> 00:28:40,640
You can't let anything happen like Rayrai, I won't allow it.

288
00:28:42,854 --> 00:28:43,880
I'm so happy.

289
00:28:45,195 --> 00:28:46,740
What do you want for dinner?

290
00:28:47,723 --> 00:28:48,724
Anything is fine.

291
00:28:49,774 --> 00:28:52,600
I'm not being nice to you, I'll cook it for my grandchild.

292
00:28:55,000 --> 00:28:56,720
Perm, take care of your wife.

293
00:28:57,142 --> 00:28:58,640
I need to go to the kitchen.

294
00:29:09,830 --> 00:29:10,920
You should get some rest.

295
00:29:12,091 --> 00:29:13,280
I will pick up your supplements.

296
00:29:47,070 --> 00:29:48,720
Tone! Tone!

297
00:29:49,107 --> 00:29:51,155
Is Shen going to be okay? What happens to Ms. Shen?

298
00:29:51,272 --> 00:29:53,342
Something huge happens to Ms. Shen, like hard to cure.

299
00:29:53,416 --> 00:29:54,800
What disease? Will she make it?

300
00:29:54,894 --> 00:29:57,080
Of course, but in 9 months.

301
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,351
What do you mean 9 months?

302
00:29:59,598 --> 00:30:00,760
(In unison) Ms. Shen is pregnant.

303
00:30:03,704 --> 00:30:04,705
Tone.

304
00:30:04,995 --> 00:30:07,320
What's with the face? You're happy for her, aren't you?

305
00:30:09,054 --> 00:30:10,055
Sure, I'm so happy.

306
00:30:10,750 --> 00:30:12,600
Our boss is pregnant. Of course, we are happy for them.

307
00:30:12,920 --> 00:30:15,400
We need to help in the kitchen.

308
00:30:15,656 --> 00:30:17,600
Khunying will celebrate tonight, big time.

309
00:30:17,854 --> 00:30:18,855
Let's go, Chan.

310
00:31:34,503 --> 00:31:35,960
Why did you look that way?

311
00:31:38,406 --> 00:31:39,640
This is not your medicine.

312
00:31:43,478 --> 00:31:45,702
These are Shen's prenatal supplements.

313
00:31:47,296 --> 00:31:48,600
She is pregnant

314
00:31:55,654 --> 00:31:57,250
with the family's first descendant.

315
00:31:58,406 --> 00:31:59,520
You're not going to smile?

316
00:32:03,075 --> 00:32:04,076
I totally forgot.

317
00:32:04,664 --> 00:32:06,200
It is hard for you to smile, isn't it?

318
00:32:06,990 --> 00:32:08,160
Let me help you.

319
00:32:09,136 --> 00:32:10,137
Come on.

320
00:32:10,538 --> 00:32:11,680
Smile, Dad.

321
00:32:13,800 --> 00:32:14,801
Smile big.

322
00:32:20,438 --> 00:32:23,000
You can eat anything you want

323
00:32:23,248 --> 00:32:24,600
so your baby will be strong.

324
00:32:28,136 --> 00:32:29,560
Thank you, Mom.

325
00:32:30,155 --> 00:32:31,323
You should go ahead and eat.

326
00:32:31,520 --> 00:32:32,890
I will take care of my wife.

327
00:32:35,250 --> 00:32:36,051
Shen,

328
00:32:36,080 --> 00:32:38,120
let me know if you're craving for something.

329
00:32:38,425 --> 00:32:39,640
I will get it for you.

330
00:32:40,203 --> 00:32:42,960
It's okay, my dish is still full.

331
00:32:44,180 --> 00:32:45,181
I'm so jealous.

332
00:32:46,376 --> 00:32:47,770
You're the center of attention now.

333
00:32:48,840 --> 00:32:50,250
If I hadn't been miscarriage,

334
00:32:50,400 --> 00:32:52,200
I would have been about to pop by now.

335
00:32:54,963 --> 00:32:56,440
It already happened

336
00:32:56,712 --> 00:32:59,000
why did you keep bringing it up, Rayrai?

337
00:33:00,851 --> 00:33:03,762
If you're so jealous of her, then you should hurry up and get pregnant.

338
00:33:04,510 --> 00:33:05,656
If you get pregnant at the same time,

339
00:33:05,747 --> 00:33:07,682
the babies will become friends.

340
00:33:09,267 --> 00:33:11,520
Sure, Mom. I will get right into it tonight.

341
00:33:13,520 --> 00:33:14,720
You need to be prepared.

342
00:33:15,240 --> 00:33:17,600
I will get you pregnant at the same time as Shen.

343
00:33:33,363 --> 00:33:34,364
What is going on?

344
00:33:35,811 --> 00:33:36,812
Right here.

345
00:33:37,480 --> 00:33:38,960
Someone spilled something on the floor

346
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:42,560
and caused me to slip down the stairs.

347
00:33:43,161 --> 00:33:45,400
My baby was gone even before it could be born.

348
00:33:47,600 --> 00:33:48,960
I'm sorry for that

349
00:33:49,619 --> 00:33:51,166
but you can start over again.

350
00:33:52,131 --> 00:33:53,132
It's easy for you to say.

351
00:33:54,132 --> 00:33:56,133
What about my completely broken heart?

352
00:33:57,235 --> 00:33:59,400
You weren't me, you wouldn't know

353
00:33:59,480 --> 00:34:01,880
how someone who lost a baby felt.

354
00:34:03,454 --> 00:34:05,840
Do you want to experience that, Shen?

355
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:08,160
So you will know how I feel.

356
00:34:08,262 --> 00:34:10,320
- You want to? Is it a great idea?
- Don't do that.

357
00:34:10,926 --> 00:34:13,680
- You want to?
- No!

358
00:34:13,827 --> 00:34:15,560
- Shen!
- You want that?

359
00:34:15,600 --> 00:34:17,120
- Huh?
- Shen!

360
00:34:17,272 --> 00:34:18,600
- Let me go.
- Shen!

361
00:34:23,664 --> 00:34:24,965
Where are you going, Shen?

362
00:34:26,624 --> 00:34:27,625
What are you trying to do?

363
00:34:30,600 --> 00:34:31,601
Perm?

364
00:34:31,893 --> 00:34:32,894
What did you do to my wife?

365
00:34:33,157 --> 00:34:34,158
Honey!

366
00:34:36,310 --> 00:34:37,311
Term!

367
00:34:42,803 --> 00:34:43,804
Please stop!

368
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:51,481
That's enough.

369
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:57,881
What is going on?

370
00:34:58,881 --> 00:35:00,120
Hey! Stop now!

371
00:35:00,640 --> 00:35:03,160
Perm! Term!

372
00:35:03,448 --> 00:35:05,800
I told you to stop! Stop!

373
00:35:07,336 --> 00:35:08,800
Stop it!

374
00:35:08,894 --> 00:35:10,080
Mr. Term, stop!

375
00:35:11,440 --> 00:35:14,000
Mr. Perm, stop!

376
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:16,440
Why did you slap my wife?

377
00:35:16,699 --> 00:35:18,700
Your wife tried to push Shen down the stairs.

378
00:35:18,740 --> 00:35:19,741
Just ask her.

379
00:35:20,830 --> 00:35:21,831
Is it true?

380
00:35:25,457 --> 00:35:26,720
I didn't mean to.

381
00:35:27,102 --> 00:35:28,800
I didn't mean to really push her.

382
00:35:29,299 --> 00:35:31,840
I just wanted her to know how I felt.

383
00:35:32,904 --> 00:35:33,905
Rayrai!

384
00:35:36,560 --> 00:35:39,400
I've never thought that you can be this cruel.

385
00:35:44,707 --> 00:35:45,708
Rayrai!

386
00:35:45,864 --> 00:35:46,665
Let me go.

387
00:35:46,680 --> 00:35:47,681
Rayrai!

388
00:35:47,870 --> 00:35:48,871
Rayrai!

389
00:35:49,840 --> 00:35:51,680
Shen? Are you okay?

390
00:35:53,475 --> 00:35:54,476
I'm fine.

391
00:36:09,451 --> 00:36:10,452
Let's go back to our room.

392
00:36:18,686 --> 00:36:19,760
Thank you, Tone.

393
00:36:21,598 --> 00:36:22,599
No problem, sir.

394
00:36:43,643 --> 00:36:45,644
How could you do that to Shen?

395
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:47,700
Are you taking her side?

396
00:36:47,862 --> 00:36:50,120
She is the one who caused our baby to be gone.

397
00:36:50,251 --> 00:36:52,450
But you can't get back at her like this.

398
00:36:53,152 --> 00:36:55,040
My mom is over the moon with this baby.

399
00:36:55,688 --> 00:36:57,240
If you become Shen's enemy,

400
00:36:57,587 --> 00:36:59,700
you will automatically become Mom's enemy, you understand me?

401
00:36:59,747 --> 00:37:02,355
What do you expect me to do?

402
00:37:04,861 --> 00:37:06,250
Like I told you before,

403
00:37:07,437 --> 00:37:08,760
you need to have another baby for Mom.

404
00:37:12,720 --> 00:37:13,721
Let me go.

405
00:37:15,035 --> 00:37:16,160
You're always like this.

406
00:37:17,200 --> 00:37:18,600
That's why nobody wants to be born from you.

407
00:37:20,107 --> 00:37:21,108
Huh?

408
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:49,043
You need to be more careful from now on.

409
00:37:49,150 --> 00:37:50,334
Stay away from Rayrai.

410
00:37:51,587 --> 00:37:53,440
If she continues to hold her grudge like this,

411
00:37:55,035 --> 00:37:57,300
I need to find a way to kick her out of this house.

412
00:38:02,603 --> 00:38:05,080
You should rest. You've been through a lot today.

413
00:38:20,718 --> 00:38:22,719
Honey,

414
00:38:26,499 --> 00:38:28,720
why are you still nice to me?

415
00:38:30,644 --> 00:38:31,962
It's because you are my wife.

416
00:38:34,547 --> 00:38:36,250
And you are pregnant.

417
00:38:37,539 --> 00:38:40,320
Who else did you expect me to be nice with?

418
00:38:42,014 --> 00:38:44,640
- You know it well that…
- Hold you tongue.

419
00:38:47,120 --> 00:38:48,560
Don't say a word.

420
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:58,100
I can't do that.

421
00:39:00,190 --> 00:39:02,360
You more you acted like nothing happened,

422
00:39:03,678 --> 00:39:04,880
the more I felt trapped.

423
00:39:07,034 --> 00:39:09,642
- Don't you want to know who is...
- Shen!

424
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:15,841
I don't want to know anything.

425
00:39:17,368 --> 00:39:18,960
I'm not questioning anything.

426
00:39:20,856 --> 00:39:21,957
I love you.

427
00:39:25,422 --> 00:39:27,700
And this baby is mine.

428
00:39:31,640 --> 00:39:33,841
Go to bed, darling.

429
00:39:52,072 --> 00:39:53,360
I love you.

430
00:40:13,560 --> 00:40:14,640
What did you say?

431
00:40:21,038 --> 00:40:23,520
It is a blessing to have a child.

432
00:40:24,387 --> 00:40:26,640
You should come here and tell him yourself.

433
00:40:45,758 --> 00:40:46,759
Tone,

434
00:40:52,870 --> 00:40:54,522
take me to see my dad.

435
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:57,761
Yes, ma'am.

436
00:41:19,160 --> 00:41:20,360
Congratulations, ma'am.

437
00:41:23,064 --> 00:41:25,520
Your baby must be so adorable.

438
00:41:28,880 --> 00:41:31,081
The first baby of you and Mr. Perm.

439
00:41:35,543 --> 00:41:36,800
You know it well that it isn't.

440
00:41:43,205 --> 00:41:44,720
What did Mr. Perm say?

441
00:41:47,558 --> 00:41:48,800
This is the weird part.

442
00:41:49,759 --> 00:41:52,120
Instead of being mad at me for being pregnant with someone else,

443
00:41:52,731 --> 00:41:55,000
he kept saying that this was his baby.

444
00:41:59,360 --> 00:42:01,361
It's because he is a best husband

445
00:42:04,448 --> 00:42:06,100
and he loves you so much.

446
00:42:09,130 --> 00:42:10,790
I'm glad the situation turned out to be just fine.

447
00:42:11,827 --> 00:42:13,740
And you feel nothing over this?

448
00:42:14,840 --> 00:42:16,960
You can even give your own child

449
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:18,501
to someone else that easily like that?

450
00:42:19,401 --> 00:42:20,800
What are you talking about?

451
00:42:22,320 --> 00:42:25,221
How could your and Mr. Perm's baby become mine?

452
00:42:25,435 --> 00:42:26,840
Stop saying that.

453
00:42:29,870 --> 00:42:31,960
I am carrying our baby.

454
00:42:33,886 --> 00:42:35,960
Since Perm came back from Penang,

455
00:42:36,100 --> 00:42:38,101
I haven't slept with him.

456
00:42:38,297 --> 00:42:40,336
I've only slept with you.

457
00:42:40,416 --> 00:42:41,960
Please don't say that.

458
00:42:43,960 --> 00:42:45,900
You're the one who told me

459
00:42:47,283 --> 00:42:49,680
that there was nothing going on between us

460
00:42:49,700 --> 00:42:50,960
more than a master and a driver.

461
00:42:53,697 --> 00:42:55,240
Did you forget all about that?

462
00:43:02,774 --> 00:43:04,640
You are Mr. Perm's wife,

463
00:43:07,107 --> 00:43:08,520
you have a great family,

464
00:43:09,840 --> 00:43:10,960
with cute children.

465
00:43:13,857 --> 00:43:14,858
In the future,

466
00:43:15,259 --> 00:43:17,520
I will drive your children to school.

467
00:43:18,520 --> 00:43:19,560
When they grow up,

468
00:43:20,200 --> 00:43:23,000
I will drive them to work.

469
00:43:25,531 --> 00:43:26,532
This is it.

470
00:43:27,760 --> 00:43:29,880
This is how our lives should be.

471
00:44:21,267 --> 00:44:22,268
Pregnant?

472
00:44:23,200 --> 00:44:24,280
Who is the father of your baby?

473
00:44:25,360 --> 00:44:27,120
What? Why did you ask her that?

474
00:44:27,587 --> 00:44:29,000
- Of course, it is…
- Lang! Shut up

475
00:44:29,088 --> 00:44:30,440
I didn't ask you.

476
00:44:31,840 --> 00:44:32,960
Who is the father of your baby?

477
00:44:33,486 --> 00:44:35,960
Of course, it is my husband's baby.

478
00:44:36,817 --> 00:44:37,840
You're lying to me.

479
00:44:39,200 --> 00:44:41,201
Tell me the truth! Who is the father?

480
00:44:42,760 --> 00:44:44,161
What do you mean by that?

481
00:44:44,805 --> 00:44:46,400
Are you accusing me of cheating on my husband?

482
00:44:46,702 --> 00:44:47,703
It isn't accusing when it is true.

483
00:44:48,424 --> 00:44:50,840
Just tell me who the father is.

484
00:44:51,457 --> 00:44:53,600
- Or you want more?
- No! Please don't!

485
00:44:57,766 --> 00:44:58,960
How did you know

486
00:44:59,486 --> 00:45:00,840
that I am not pregnant with Perm?

487
00:45:02,147 --> 00:45:03,320
That son of a bitch

488
00:45:03,630 --> 00:45:06,360
has been sterile since he worked in Penang.

489
00:45:30,720 --> 00:45:31,721
Do you want money?

490
00:46:29,320 --> 00:46:30,880
How did you know about all of this?

491
00:46:31,383 --> 00:46:33,720
I am his wife and I didn't even know.

492
00:46:34,320 --> 00:46:36,800
I sent those guys to beat him up.

493
00:46:40,821 --> 00:46:41,822
Dad?

494
00:46:44,235 --> 00:46:45,800
Why did you do that for?

495
00:46:47,463 --> 00:46:49,760
He was tricky to me so I gave him a taste of his own medicine.

496
00:46:53,320 --> 00:46:55,560
I checked every sack of my rice by myself.

497
00:46:56,139 --> 00:46:58,520
How could it be a trouble?

498
00:47:00,160 --> 00:47:01,720
I have no idea about that.

499
00:47:02,307 --> 00:47:04,628
The quality control department informed me that

500
00:47:05,043 --> 00:47:07,144
your rice hasn't quite reached the criteria.

501
00:47:08,371 --> 00:47:09,800
We can't export your product.

502
00:47:09,857 --> 00:47:12,280
Otherwise, it will ruin Siam's reputation.

503
00:47:17,017 --> 00:47:18,482
What do I need to do

504
00:47:19,360 --> 00:47:20,920
to get it passed smoothly?

505
00:47:25,075 --> 00:47:26,200
Do I need to provide

506
00:47:29,240 --> 00:47:31,160
hot tea fee'?

507
00:47:34,240 --> 00:47:36,680
Perhaps, it can help moving it along faster.

508
00:47:41,027 --> 00:47:45,000
I've never expected the 'hot tea fee' from anyone.

509
00:47:50,203 --> 00:47:51,480
Earlier,

510
00:47:52,200 --> 00:47:53,680
when I walked into your place,

511
00:47:53,983 --> 00:47:56,760
I saw your daughter. She was quite a pretty girl.

512
00:47:58,120 --> 00:47:59,800
How old is she this year?

513
00:48:01,400 --> 00:48:02,401
She is 21 years old.

514
00:48:05,680 --> 00:48:07,181
Well, I guess

515
00:48:08,080 --> 00:48:10,081
she is old enough to get married. Am I right?

516
00:48:17,528 --> 00:48:18,963
People have known it well that

517
00:48:19,256 --> 00:48:21,880
Lord Sampanpanich from Ministry of Commerce

518
00:48:22,227 --> 00:48:24,100
looks so innocent but

519
00:48:24,526 --> 00:48:27,920
he keeps extorting 'the hot tea fee' from merchants like us.

520
00:48:28,480 --> 00:48:30,160
He is getting richer and richer.

521
00:48:31,928 --> 00:48:34,960
But he didn't ask money from me.

522
00:48:36,123 --> 00:48:37,600
It's because you have a beautiful daughter

523
00:48:38,086 --> 00:48:39,880
and she is way more valuable than money.

524
00:48:40,534 --> 00:48:41,723
He must have known that

525
00:48:41,808 --> 00:48:44,480
you wouldn't let your daughter marry a Thai man.

526
00:48:45,320 --> 00:48:47,760
So he started to mess with your exported product.

527
00:48:48,560 --> 00:48:50,100
Instead of asking you for money,

528
00:48:50,960 --> 00:48:53,240
he asked for your daughter instead.

529
00:48:54,040 --> 00:48:55,041
He is a real piece of work.

530
00:49:01,504 --> 00:49:04,000
I sent someone to beat him up in Penang

531
00:49:04,870 --> 00:49:06,166
but they went too far.

532
00:49:06,486 --> 00:49:09,540
I heard the news from the clinic he went to

533
00:49:10,160 --> 00:49:12,400
that his personal part

534
00:49:13,187 --> 00:49:14,440
can't be working anymore.

535
00:49:15,320 --> 00:49:16,321
Don't you think

536
00:49:16,640 --> 00:49:18,400
that you're too cruel for doing that?

537
00:49:18,491 --> 00:49:19,520
Cruel? What do you mean?

538
00:49:19,904 --> 00:49:21,960
He was the one who started to be crafty with me.

539
00:49:23,400 --> 00:49:25,301
If my business hadn't been in trouble,

540
00:49:25,401 --> 00:49:28,040
I wouldn't have let you marry him, never.

541
00:49:29,024 --> 00:49:30,025
So I was just

542
00:49:30,645 --> 00:49:33,440
a pawn in your business, that's it?

543
00:49:33,648 --> 00:49:36,880
So what? You are a girl.

544
00:49:37,158 --> 00:49:40,240
This is the only way to help the business.

545
00:49:41,856 --> 00:49:45,920
I shouldn't have been born to a cruel father like you.

546
00:49:47,590 --> 00:49:49,046
Hey! Where are you going?

547
00:49:49,995 --> 00:49:52,640
You haven't told me who the father is.

548
00:49:52,902 --> 00:49:54,280
Why do you want to know?

549
00:49:54,651 --> 00:49:57,040
- Come back here, who is the father?
- No!

550
00:49:57,600 --> 00:49:58,601
Let me go.

551
00:49:58,742 --> 00:50:01,080
Anybody's there! Come inside, quick!

552
00:50:02,320 --> 00:50:03,321
Catch her!

553
00:50:04,475 --> 00:50:05,476
What are you doing?

554
00:50:06,600 --> 00:50:09,440
The baby is not your husband's.

555
00:50:09,542 --> 00:50:10,598
It is an illegitimate child.

556
00:50:10,950 --> 00:50:11,851
In the future,

557
00:50:11,877 --> 00:50:14,320
he could use this fact against me and my business.

558
00:50:14,784 --> 00:50:15,785
We need to get rid of it,

559
00:50:15,885 --> 00:50:17,640
so it won't be a cause of trouble to my business in the future.

560
00:50:17,839 --> 00:50:20,240
No! I won't let you!

561
00:50:21,563 --> 00:50:23,120
- Let her go!
- Take her upstairs!

562
00:50:23,456 --> 00:50:25,480
Come on! Take her upstairs!

563
00:50:27,190 --> 00:50:30,440
Sir, please think of the baby.

564
00:50:30,590 --> 00:50:33,120
- It is your grandchild.
- It is not my grandchild.

565
00:50:34,438 --> 00:50:36,680
You need to brew the medicine. Go!

566
00:50:45,000 --> 00:50:46,001
Hey, you.

567
00:50:47,755 --> 00:50:49,960
Ms. Shen will have dinner at home.

568
00:50:50,219 --> 00:50:52,840
She told you to go home. We will give her a ride later.

569
00:50:54,958 --> 00:50:55,959
She did?

570
00:50:57,160 --> 00:51:00,000
Dad, please don't hurt my baby.

571
00:51:00,158 --> 00:51:01,960
It doesn't know anything.

572
00:51:02,040 --> 00:51:04,000
Please let it live.

573
00:51:05,128 --> 00:51:06,760
I beg you, please.

574
00:51:08,424 --> 00:51:09,425
Shut up.

575
00:51:19,888 --> 00:51:21,360
You need to tell your husband

576
00:51:21,843 --> 00:51:24,440
that you fell and you's miscarriage.

577
00:51:24,720 --> 00:51:25,721
You hear me?

578
00:51:36,342 --> 00:51:39,160
Lang, don't hurt the baby.

579
00:51:39,366 --> 00:51:41,560
You told me that you wanted me to have a baby

580
00:51:41,600 --> 00:51:43,460
and you would help me raise it.

581
00:51:43,835 --> 00:51:46,160
Lang, pour the medicine down her throat.

582
00:51:51,987 --> 00:51:54,360
- No! Don't do it!
- Come here, open your mouth!

583
00:51:54,520 --> 00:51:55,521
Open your mouth!

584
00:51:56,904 --> 00:51:57,960
Drink it!

585
00:51:58,920 --> 00:51:59,921
Swallow it!

586
00:52:00,102 --> 00:52:01,203
Swallow it!

587
00:52:02,107 --> 00:52:03,108
More!

588
00:52:03,471 --> 00:52:04,880
That's it!

589
00:52:08,269 --> 00:52:10,400
Lang, you need to watch her

590
00:52:10,712 --> 00:52:12,040
until the baby comes out

591
00:52:12,680 --> 00:52:13,920
and bring it for me to see.

592
00:52:24,920 --> 00:52:26,842
What are you waiting for? Get out of here!

593
00:53:24,024 --> 00:53:25,025
Easy there.

594
00:53:38,125 --> 00:53:39,522
You're done?

595
00:53:40,651 --> 00:53:41,652
Yes.

596
00:53:42,416 --> 00:53:43,417
Let me see.

597
00:53:47,080 --> 00:53:48,457
Throw away somewhere far from home.

598
00:53:48,758 --> 00:53:51,320
It's waste from woman and it's inauspicious.

599
00:53:51,642 --> 00:53:52,643
Yes, sir.

600
00:53:54,576 --> 00:53:55,577
Shen,

601
00:53:56,187 --> 00:53:58,006
you can't make the same mistake and get pregnant again.

602
00:53:58,336 --> 00:54:00,640
What if I do, what are you going to do?

603
00:54:00,710 --> 00:54:02,440
I will force you into another abortion.

604
00:54:02,700 --> 00:54:04,701
Miss, stop arguing with him.

605
00:54:05,040 --> 00:54:06,320
You should go home and rest.

606
00:54:15,523 --> 00:54:16,722
Lang, take care.

607
00:54:17,840 --> 00:54:20,597
I will. You need to take care of yourself

608
00:54:21,750 --> 00:54:23,520
and the baby inside of you, okay?

609
00:54:51,712 --> 00:54:52,713
Tone.

610
00:54:54,590 --> 00:54:55,591
Yes, sir?

611
00:54:56,355 --> 00:54:57,356
Where is Shen?

612
00:54:57,907 --> 00:55:00,040
She will stay for dinner at her dad's house.

613
00:55:01,328 --> 00:55:02,329
We need to talk.

614
00:55:03,072 --> 00:55:04,073
Yes, sir.

615
00:55:19,877 --> 00:55:21,990
What are you waiting for? Get out of here!

616
00:55:38,097 --> 00:55:39,098
Miss?

617
00:55:40,947 --> 00:55:41,948
Miss!

618
00:55:43,422 --> 00:55:44,840
Please stop crying.

619
00:55:45,304 --> 00:55:47,160
I didn't give you any hemagogue.

620
00:55:54,195 --> 00:55:55,196
You didn't?

621
00:55:57,342 --> 00:55:58,720
You didn't give it to me?

622
00:55:59,520 --> 00:56:00,521
I didn't.

623
00:56:00,787 --> 00:56:02,800
I prepared pig's blood to fool your dad.

624
00:56:03,171 --> 00:56:04,280
He can't tell the different.

625
00:56:06,160 --> 00:56:07,350
Thank you, Lang.

626
00:56:08,060 --> 00:56:09,161
Thank you.

627
00:56:19,992 --> 00:56:21,700
What should I do next?

628
00:56:22,557 --> 00:56:24,120
I really can't find my way out of this.

629
00:56:25,650 --> 00:56:27,651
Stop overthinking already.

630
00:56:28,344 --> 00:56:30,085
You can go back to your husband.

631
00:56:32,542 --> 00:56:34,200
You're carrying someone else's child

632
00:56:34,243 --> 00:56:35,880
and he is willing to accept it as a father.

633
00:56:36,480 --> 00:56:39,000
It shows that he loves you so much.

634
00:56:51,563 --> 00:56:53,200
What is on your mind?

635
00:56:55,142 --> 00:56:58,200
Do you think he knows who the father of my child is?

636
00:57:00,054 --> 00:57:01,360
Maybe he knows.

637
00:57:02,200 --> 00:57:04,590
Like I said, your husband loves you so much

638
00:57:04,723 --> 00:57:07,560
and he must adore Tone. So he is fine with it.

639
00:57:07,857 --> 00:57:09,600
You're way too optimistic, Lang.

640
00:57:10,886 --> 00:57:13,680
Why do I feel like something just doesn't add up?

641
00:57:59,326 --> 00:58:00,480
- Chan.
- Yes, ma'am?

642
00:58:01,157 --> 00:58:02,240
Have you seen Tone?

643
00:58:02,920 --> 00:58:04,880
I saw him in the gardern with Mr. Perm earlier.

644
00:58:28,063 --> 00:58:29,500
I don't want to trouble you any longer.

645
00:58:33,251 --> 00:58:35,240
You're not gonna wait until Ms. Shen gives birth?

646
00:58:35,800 --> 00:58:37,560
In case there is an accident like what happened to Ms. Rayrai.

647
00:58:37,827 --> 00:58:39,828
- I could help.
- No need!

648
00:58:39,830 --> 00:58:41,000
Your job here is done.

649
00:58:43,070 --> 00:58:44,471
And I believe that from now on

650
00:58:44,500 --> 00:58:45,801
I will take the best care of Shen

651
00:58:45,811 --> 00:58:47,440
and nothing bad will happen for sure.

652
00:58:48,463 --> 00:58:49,840
- But Mr. Perm…
- Go back to Penang already.

653
00:58:59,878 --> 00:59:00,879
What's the matter?

654
00:59:03,499 --> 00:59:04,640
Don't tell me that

655
00:59:05,515 --> 00:59:07,040
you want to stay here

656
00:59:10,011 --> 00:59:12,060
because you fall in love with my wife for real.

657
00:59:15,096 --> 00:59:16,097
No, sir.

658
00:59:17,624 --> 00:59:19,120
I've never loved her.

659
00:59:24,440 --> 00:59:26,200
This is just another job for me.

660
00:59:40,275 --> 00:59:41,440
This is the rest of your payment.

661
00:59:46,326 --> 00:59:47,920
This should cover your sperm fee.

662
00:59:55,323 --> 00:59:56,400
Don't worry

663
00:59:57,200 --> 00:59:58,201
about your baby.

664
00:59:58,939 --> 01:00:01,680
I will take the best care of it as if it is my own baby.

665
01:00:03,958 --> 01:00:04,959
Got it, sir.

666
01:00:24,040 --> 01:00:25,720
I will start over

667
01:00:26,443 --> 01:00:27,760
with my baby

668
01:00:28,443 --> 01:00:29,962
with the life that I choose.

669
01:00:34,960 --> 01:00:37,080
Nobody can control me anymore.

670
01:00:37,920 --> 01:00:39,680
Mister? Can you speed up?

671
01:00:40,480 --> 01:00:41,481
Ms. Shen.

672
01:00:42,400 --> 01:00:45,080
Is this where you work?

673
01:00:46,560 --> 01:00:48,640
A make love spot for both of you.
